@startuml flow
title System Sequence Diagram - TEMPLATE

actor User as U
participant System as S
participant ExternalService

U -> S : 1. User triggers action
S -> S : 2. System validates data
S -> ExternalService : 3. Fetch required info
ExternalService --> S : 4. Return data
S --> U : 5. Return response

alt Invalid data
    S --> U : Error message
else Valid data
    S -> S : Continue processing
end

loop While condition is true
    U -> S : Repeated request
    S --> U : Repeated response
end

@enduml
